# Funkce, kter zprostedkovv pipojen ke Spotify API
def init_spotipy():
    scope = "user-library-read user-top-read"
    redirect_uri = "http://localhost:8888/callback"
    return spotipy.Spotify(auth_manager=SpotifyOAuth(scope=scope, client_id=my_id, client_secret=my_token, redirect_uri=redirect_uri))
In [5]:
# Tato funkce vrt seznam vech umlc

def get_top_artists(sp, limit, _range):
    artists_json = sp.current_user_top_artists(limit=limit, time_range=_range)
    
    artists_set = set()
    for artist in artists_json["items"]:
        artist_name = artist["name"]
        artists_set.add(artist_name)
    return artists_set
In [33]:
# Hledn zem umlc v databzi MusicBrainz

music_api.set_useragent(app="Mapping top artists areas", version="0.1")
def find_countries(artists_names):
    countries = dict()
    not_found = []
    
    for artist_name in artists_names:
        # Ze jmna umlce zjist jeho ID
        try:
            artist_id = music_api.search_artists(artist_name)["artist-list"][0]["id"]
        except Exception:
            print("Umlec nebyl nalezen v databzi MusicBrainz")
            continue
        
        # Najde umlce podle ID
        try:
            result = music_api.get_artist_by_id(artist_id)
        except WebServiceError as e:
            print(f"Nco se pokazilo pi hledn umlce na MusicBrainz.\n {e}")
            continue
        
        # U nalezenho umlce zjist zemi
        try:
            countries[artist_name] = result["artist"]["area"]["name"]
        except Exception:
            print(f"Pro umlce {artist_name} se nenala zem")
            not_found.append(artist_name)
            continue
            
    # Vype vechny umlce, u kterch nebyla nalezena jejich zem
    if not_found != []:
        print("Pod tuto buku vlote (zamte ZEM za skuten stt):")
        for item in not_found:
            print(f'artists_countries["{item}"] = "ZEM"')
    return countries

# Ulo vsledek do souboru
def save_artists_countries(artists_dict):
    with open("Data/artists_countries.csv", "w", encoding="utf-8") as file:
        for artist, country in artists_dict.items():
            file.write(f"{artist},{country}\n")

# Do tabulky jednotlivch zem pid nov sloupec, kter obsahuje umlce z dan zem
def add_artists(row):
    if row["NAME"] in grouped.groups:
        row["Artists"] = grouped.get_group(row["NAME"])["Artist"].values
    else:
        row["Artists"] = None
    return row

# Vytvoen vsledn tabulky

# Tabulku umlc rozdl do skupin podle zem
grouped = artists_df.groupby(["Country"])

# Dopln do tabulky zem poty umlc
merged_countries = countries.merge(grouped.count(), left_on="NAME", right_on="Country", how="left").fillna(0)

merged_countries["Artist"] = merged_countries["Artist"].astype(int)
merged_countries = merged_countries.rename(columns={"Artist": "Artists_count"})

# Do tabulky se zemmi dopln sloupec se jmny umlc, kte z dan zem pochzej
merged_countries = merged_countries.apply(add_artists, axis=1)

merged_countries[merged_countries["NAME"] == "Czech Republic"] # Otestovn, e ve probhlo v podku  vype dek pro esko

from shapely.geometry.point import Point
from matplotlib import rc
from matplotlib.backend_bases import MouseButton
rc('text', usetex=True)  # Toto je nutn pro formtovn popisk


# Po kliknut my najde v tabulce dek zem, na kterou bylo kliknuto 
def find_row(point):
    for index, row in merged_countries.iterrows():
        if row.geometry.contains(point):
            return row

# Po kliknut vytvo popisek / nebo ho smae (zobrazen popisku trv pomrn dlouho)
def make_label(event, fig, text):
    if event.button is MouseButton.LEFT:
        # Pokud bylo kliknuto levm tlatkem, vytvo se na pozici kurzoru nov bod a podle nho se v tabulce najde zem
        clicked_point = Point(event.xdata, event.ydata)
        row = find_row(clicked_point)
        
        # Pokud se nala zem
        if row is not None:
            if row["Artists"] is not None: # Kdy v dan zemi nejsou dn umlci, je jej nzev podtren
                text.set_text(r"$\textbf{\underline{" + row["NAME"] + "}}$" + "\n" + "\n".join(row["Artists"]))
            else:
                # Do popisku se nape text
                text.set_text(r"$\textbf{" + row["NAME"] + "}$" + "\nNo artist")
            text.set_position((event.xdata, event.ydata)) # Umstn popisku na pozici myi
            text.set_visible(True) # Zviditelnn popisku
    else:
        text.set_visible(False)
        # Pokud bylo kliknuto prostednm nebo pravm tlatkem, popisek se zneviditeln 
        
    fig.canvas.draw()  # Mapa se mus vykreslit znovu, aby se zobrazil popisek

%matplotlib auto

# Msto pro graf
fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(18, 16))

# Vytvo se objekt popisku - pro vechny popisky se pouv jenom jeden, kter se pesouv a pepisuje
text_object = ax.text(0.0, 0.0, "", style='normal', fontsize=17,
        bbox={'facecolor': 'red', 'alpha': 0.9, 'pad': 10})
text_object.set_visible(False)

# Nastav, e po kliknut myi se spust funkce make_label()
plt.connect("button_press_event", lambda event: make_label(event, fig, text_object))

# Vytvo mapu
merged_countries.plot(ax=ax, column="Artists_count", 
                      cmap="Greys", edgecolor="black", 
                      linewidth=0.2, legend=True,
                      legend_kwds={"label":"Poet oblbench umlc", "orientation": "vertical"}
                     )

plt.axis("off")  # Zru popisky os x a y 

# Vytvo seznam hodnot, kter se zobraz v menu
area_options = ["world"] + sorted(merged_countries[merged_countries.Artists_count > 0].NAME.to_list())

@widgets.interact  # Vytvo menu, z kterho lze vybrat zemi, kter se m na map piblit
def choose_area(Country=area_options):
    if Country != "world": 
        selected_data = merged_countries[merged_countries.NAME == Country]
    else: # Pi kliknut na monost world se zobraz vehny stty
        selected_data = merged_countries
        
    # Piblen na danou zemi (funguje jenom pi sputn v samostatnm okn)
    minx, miny, maxx, maxy = selected_data.total_bounds
    ax.set_xlim(minx * 0.95, maxx * 1.05)
    ax.set_ylim(miny * 0.95, maxy * 1.05)
    
    # Zobraz tabulku s umlci z dan zem
    display(artists_df[artists_df.Country.isin(selected_data.NAME)].groupby("Country").apply(lambda a: a.reindex(index=a["Artist"]).drop(["Country", "Artist"], axis=1)[:]))
